Articles.Content:
Hello,

yesterday i installed KSp from Steam. I paused playing the game for a couple of month. Using ckan i downloaded some mods i used in the past. So KSP crashes when the Program starts to load Squad Parts. Like Antennas, Decouplers, Thermometers... I deleted the cfg Files and launch KSP again until the next Squad Part is causing a crash.

Thank you for your help in advance.

 

Regards

Ulf
